himself to their inmost soul,

00:46:49.480 --> 00:46:52.440
and who fills it with humility
and joy with confidence

00:46:52.440 --> 00:46:56.624
and love, who renders them
incapable of any other end

00:46:56.624 --> 00:46:57.165
than himself.

