concomitant variability.

00:49:58.770 --> 00:50:02.390
The other possible
problem with these studies

00:50:02.390 --> 00:50:03.920
is that they
represent what's been

00:50:03.920 --> 00:50:06.260
called the ecological fallacy.

00:50:06.260 --> 00:50:12.290
Ecological fallacy is
sampling at the wrong scale.

00:50:12.290 --> 00:50:14.300
And by the way, my
initial training

00:50:14.300 --> 00:50:15.560
was in ecology actually.

00:50:15.560 --> 00:50:17.330
