NICK SHELTA: Wow.

01:00:11.350 --> 01:00:12.480
Thank you for that.

01:00:12.480 --> 01:00:13.290
DR. JEFF SCHLOSS:
Great to be with you.

01:00:13.290 --> 01:00:15.165
